short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Next gen ERD: explore and analyze your SQL database schema

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Explore and analyze your SQL database schema like never before with Azimutt, with full privacy.

Azimutt is a dynamic entity-relationship diagram which stays relevant for database up to 1000 tables:
- choose tables and columns to display
- follow relations (in and out)
- find a path between two tables
- get insights on your schema design and keep it consistent

This extension keep Azimutt easily accessible:
- one click schema access
- explore any github hosted database schema in Azimutt
